{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"162857-clever-cat","title":"Paka mwerevu","description":"Safi is a clever cat! Find out more!","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ursula Nafula"],"illustrators":["Catherine Groenewald"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/162857-clever-cat"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/253186/size3/12d218fb4d4baa7c1463938230643b3c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/253186/size6/12d218fb4d4baa7c1463938230643b3c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227766/size6/3f0a10d9f57cdc0e4ed478bfbbba72c2.jpg","text":"Bwana Kio anaishi kijijini kwetu. Ana paka anayeitwa Safi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227769/size6/95735b081c3dd7ebbe16b0285021c5c1.jpg","text":"Bwana Kio anapoenda kazini, anauacha mlango wazi.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227772/size6/bf49cfdc2d659ee69b64a281734cab4a.jpg","text":"Safi anaketi mlangoni na kuilinda nyumba.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227773/size6/b838a7aeba7c493bb274683ef0f2afd6.jpg","text":"Mbwa wa jirani akiikaribia nyumba, Safi anamtisha.\nYuko tayari kumkwaruza kwa kucha zake.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227777/size6/c036a0fa3c9c304584630ddddb43d763.jpg","text":"Mbwa anatoroka na kurudi kwao.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227779/size6/0e3e6ba33db19a81f4e7f2d5065bfc60.jpg","text":"Jirani akiugusa malango wa nyumba, Safi anamwona. Yuko tayari kumkwaruza.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227781/size6/c9bf6b35e3695457c7485cdbc68b0f48.jpg","text":"Jirani anageuka haraka na kwenda zake.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227783/size6/68a26b0816f5fb2ef5ca4adfad800405.jpg","text":"Safi anapohisi njaa, anajua la kufanya.\nAnaufunga mlango, kisha anaenda kula.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227785/size6/40945659bcd45363388c6ff3c81ad186.jpg","text":"Safi anakula kutoka bakuli lake la bluu.\nAnakipenda chakula chake sana.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227789/size6/90909018c331bf1fdaec16a55ba13b25.jpg","text":"Akimaliza, anaruka juu ya sofa na kulala. \"Purr! Purr! Purr!\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227790/size6/73f41de8439de0d7dbddb9297ea39fff.jpg","text":"Bwana Kio anarudi nyumbani jioni.\nSafi anajinyoosha kwa furaha na kumlaki.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/227792/size6/36ebafd8316feac19fea943d03c800f0.jpg","text":"Bwana Kio na Safi wanaketi sebuleni.\nKila mmoja anasoma gazeti.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":109}}